Summary: Defines a height field for GPU particles to collide with in 3D space.

GPUParticlesCollisionHeightField3D

Inherits: GPUParticlesCollision3D < GPUParticlesCollisionBase3D < Node3D < Node < Object

A height field for GPU particles to collide with in 3D space. This node allows you to define a height map that particles will interact with, creating effects like particles flowing over uneven surfaces.
